and cry, "Yes, I did it. I confess."

1218
01:32:50,231 --> 01:32:52,941
By the way,
add a life term to my sentence."

1219
01:32:53,150 --> 01:32:55,944
With Tommy's testimony,
I can get a new trial.

1220
01:32:56,153 --> 01:32:58,613
That's assuming Blatch is still there.

1221
01:32:58,823 --> 01:33:00,782
Chances are, he'd be released by now.

1222
01:33:00,992 --> 01:33:05,579
They'd have his last known address, names
of relatives. It's a chance, isn't it?

1223
01:33:07,915 --> 01:33:09,666
How can you be so obtuse?

1224
01:33:10,585 --> 01:33:11,835
What?

1225
01:33:13,087 --> 01:33:14,546
What did you call me?

1226
01:33:14,755 --> 01:33:16,506
Obtuse. Is it deliberate?

1227
01:33:16,841 --> 01:33:18,341
